title: Unisonic Ascension - Sleep Easy Theta to Delta [FLAC]
description:
Enter a deep meditation, or sleep easy, with this sweeping melodic drone and binaural beats. The binaural beats and drone tempo, ramps down form a high Theta state, to a low Delta state. The full track starts and holds at 7Hz Theta for 10 min. And then glides down over 60 min to 1Hz Delta where it holds for the last 10 Min. Listen with stereo headphones. 

87 min
